description:
My name is **Meow**, the cat! I was once a perfectly normal cat, a pet of a wonderful owner. That was before I fell through a portal and was trapped into the Blockchain, where I heard a rumor that there are 600 unique 1/1 combinations of me formed in all sorts of outfits and scenarios. My goal is to find a lovely home for all the stray Meow's I find in my journey. 

All drops will occur on a frequent basis & released in batches. 
Releases will be announced on Instagram, Discord & Twitter.

The first 100 Pixel Meow's will be priced at 0.01 ETH, with prices stepping up every release.
Rare Meow's will be in the form of gifs & will contain multiple tails. Meow's evolution might appear one day.

 **❤️ A portion of the initial Pixel Meow's sales will go towards stray cats shelter**

**Follow Meow's journey, release news and announcements on [Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/pixelmeowsofficial/), [Twitter](https://twitter.com/PixelMeows) & [Discord](https://discord.gg/qs8AHbGwSU)**
name: PixelMeows
